in the healthcare space. And correspondingly, you have a little bit of different attitudes

00:18:01.319 --> 00:18:06.760
on where you want to start. That said, I think you do end up investing a lot more in risk control

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:12.920
frameworks, security review processes, et cetera, in order to make those viable, safe and secure.

00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:17.800
Because at the end of the day, patient safety and scientific integrity is paramount to what we do.

00:18:18.520 --> 00:18:24.520
